## Early game

**Tessera** on Venus (Defense) is a short, low-level Corpus Defense on one of
Circuits' two signature planets, making it an easy repeat farm for a fresh
account. Circuits drop from the enemies you kill, so a Resource Drop Booster
and a loot frame add Circuits to every wave you clear.

## Mid & late game

**Gabii** on Ceres (Dark Sector Survival) is the wiki's higher-drop-rate
endgame pick, with Steel Path squads running it for longer per rotation than
a standard mission. Circuits are a common enemy drop, so the Grineer density
on Steel Path plus a Resource Drop Booster and a Nekros loot squad make this
a strong endless farm. Deploying a Titan Extractor on Venus or Ceres is also
a passive way to stock up Circuits without actively farming.

